  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">A new analysis method using Bragg curve spectroscopy for a Multi-purpose Active-target Particle Telescope for radiation monitoring</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
